BTCplex is an open source Bitcoin block chain browser written in **[Go](http://golang.org/)** ([source code available on GitHub](https://github.com/tsileo/btcplex)).

## Blockchain Explorer

### Web Interface

BTCplex allows you to search and navigate the [[blockchain|Block_chain]].

* Browse [[blocks|Blocks]] and [[transactions|Transactions]].
* Check [[addresses|Address]] balance history.
* Search for blocks, transactions, and addresses.

### API

BTCplex provides a full-featured JSON API to access data pragmatically.

* A [REST API](http://docs.btcplex.com/api_rest/) for acessing blocks, transactions and addresses balance.
* A [[BlockExplorer.com|BlockExplorer.com]] compatible [plain text query API](http://docs.btcplex.com/api_query/).
* Few [server-sent events endpoints](http://docs.btcplex.com/api_sse/) to monitor addresses, unconfirmed transactions, and new blocks.

